data.description: Welcome Home to Tranquil Living in Grand Haven Township! Discover the potential awaiting you in this charming Ranch Style Home, nestled in the heart of Grand Haven Township. Perfectly situated close to Mercury Park, a scenic bike path, esteemed schools, and convenient shopping, this location offers the epitome of suburban bliss. This delightful abode boasts 3 cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen and dining area showcase elegant tile flooring, creating a seamless flow of style and functionality. Entertain with ease in the inviting living room, featuring a convenient slider that beckons you to the patio. Picture yourself enjoying morning coffee or evening gatherings while overlooking the expansive fenced backyard, complete with a handy storage shed for all your outdoor essentials. As you approach, be greeted by the enchanting decorative white fence, a charming prelude to the warmth and comfort found within. With just a touch of tender loving care, this residence is poised to become your haven of happiness and cherished memories. Don't miss out on the opportunity to embark on your journey of homeownership in this idyllic setting. Schedule your private tour today and let your dream of owning a piece of paradise begin! Call now to make this home yours before it's gone!
